data.title: André Vos
data.meta_description: André Neal Vos is a former South African rugby union player who played as a loose forward for Eastern Province, Queensland Reds (Australia), The Cats, The Lions and Harlequins (England) until his retirement in 2007.
data.text:
André Neal Vos (born 9 January 1975) is a former South African rugby union player who played as a loose forward for Eastern Province (South Africa), Queensland Reds (Australia),[1] The Cats, The Lions and Harlequins (England) until his retirement in 2007.
